What is the output of the following code?

```java
public class Test {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    int[][][] data = {{{1, 2}, {3, 4}},
      {{5, 6}, {7, 8}}};

    System.out.print(ttt(data[0]));
  }

  public static int ttt(int[][] m) {
    int v = m[0][0];

    for (int i = 0; i < m.length; i++)
      for (int j = 0; j < m[i].length; j++)
        if (v < m[i][j])
          v = m[i][j];

    return v;
  }
}
```
